title: Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Crunch Bench (BFAB20R), Lower & Upper Abdominal Muscles Workout Machine For Home Gym, Red/Black
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Benches › Adjustable Benches
description: Product DescriptionPerform a variety of ab exercises easily, effectively, and safely with the Body-Solid Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Bench (BFAB20). The adjustable, ergonomic AB crunch bench seat can be adjusted into 3 different positions to accommodate a wide range of heights and motion. The AB workout bench seat is angled at 45-degrees and reclines to 2 different 5-degree angles for a wide range of motion. This abdominal bench with adjustable length, textured grip handles, standard weight post, and 2-position footrests make it is comfortable and easy to perform exercises such as ab crunches and knee raises. When assembled the Body-Solid Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Bench (BFAB20) measures 64 by 11 by 46 inches (L x W x H). The frame is backed by the Best Fitness 3-year Warranty and the parts are backed by a 1 year warranty.Amazon.comMake any time crunch time with the Best Fitness BFAB20 semi-recumbent ab crunch. Unlike some other ab machines--which require the agility of an acrobat to be thoroughly effective--the BFAB20 puts you in a comfortable seated position without sacrificing your workout efficiency. The ergonomically designed machine is built to help you tighten up your midsection, strengthen your back, and improve your core stability, with your choice of toning your lower abs with knees raises or your upper abs with abdominal crunches. To perform ab crunches, simply use the upholstered upper back support, textured grip handles, and standard weight post. Performing knee raises is just as easy thanks to the adjustable-length, two-position footrests. Add in a three-position upholstered seat--which starts at 45 degrees but offers two additional 5-degree reclining positions--and you have everything you need to design an effective ab regimen in the comfort of your own home.  The BFAB20 is an essential workout accessory because your core is where all your body movements originate. Your abdominal muscles support and protect your internal organs and aid in breathing, especially when you exhale. The abs also team up with your back muscles to control trunk motions, such as twisting and bending. The BFAB20 takes the next step by also strengthening and toning the front of the thighs and increasing hip flexibility. The end results include a flatter stomach, better defined abs, well-developed obliques, a more upright posture, and greater support for your spine. Other features include a 1.75-inch upholstered seat, a durable powder-coated finish, and safety pins and bolts that allow for easy disassembly or permanent setup. The BFAB20 measures 22 by 46 by 64 inches (W x H x D) and carries a three-year warranty.
features: "INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Best FItness by Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life."

"ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED: This ergonomically designed machine is built to help you tighten up your midsection, strengthen your back and improve your core stability. Its dual functionality lets you target your lower abs with knee raises and your upper abs with abdominal crunches."

"45-DEGREE WORKOUT SEAT: This machine can provide total ab workout from a comfortable seated position. The 45-degree seat angle puts you in position to isolate your abdominal muscles, for a more efficient workout. Plus, with two additional 5-degree reclining positions, you'll be ideally supported for an entire range of core exercises."

"ADJUSTABLE FOOT RESTS: The adjustable foot rests can be adjusted up to 13 different positions including 3 height adjustments and 10 slope level adjustments providing maximum comfort, stability and most importantly, target the right muscle groups for desired results. Plus, with the ergonomic handlebars and padded cushion, you'll be able to get the most out of your session without sacrificing on comfort."

"DIMENSIONS: This ab machine is perfect for those just starting out their core-training journey or for more experienced athletes, as the adjustable tension knob can be easily adjusted to match your preferred challenge level. The measures 22 x 46 x 64 inches and carries a three-year warrantty on the frame and 1 year on ALL parts."

features: 💪【HEAVY DUTY & STABLE CONSTRUCTION】: SPART 2023 New Style Seated Row Machine is made of heavy duty solid steel and premium heavy coating for the long term use.The stable construction of this back machine ensures great safety and comfort during intense workouts, can hold up to 440 LBS.The special incline design of the chest pad and the seat position make this machine more ergonomic, which allows you to maximize potential and achieve most training results of back muscles.

💪【360° ROTARY & ADJUSTABLE DUAL GRIP HANDLES】: This back workout machine has two different styles of grip handles. The fixed grips are for precise stimulation, similar to barbell and T-bar row machines. The 360 degree rotary handles allow you to rotate your arms naturally for a comfortable motion when rowing, which also helps prevent strain and injury. Besides, these fully rotating grips can be aslo adjusted by left and right to accommodate trainers with different shoulder widths.

Beasides, you are also free to adjust the width of your grip and the width of your arms to target different back muscle groups, which helps you to complete various trainings and achieve most exercise goals.

💪【ENLARGED CHEST & SEATED PADS】: According to the actual needs, we have enlarged the chest pad and seated pad, which are much larger than the others on the market. The dimension of the chest pad is 13.8“ x9.8" and the seated pad is 13.8" x 10.5", will offer great comfort while use. With these attachments, you are able to do biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls.Compared to traditional cable row machines, it can be applied to a wider range of upper body training, resulting in stronger stimulation of your back muscles, including your lats, rhomboids and traps. Don't hesitate to join us to get started on your back day!

✅【WHY CHOOSE SPART】: The sizes of the assembled seated row machine are 63.9 in(L) x 37.3 in(W) x 43.8 in(H), total gross weight: 91 lbs. Fits both 1inch standard and 2inch olympic weight plates, the 2inch detachable adapters are included. We offer 1-year warranty and lifetime customer service for this machine. From the manufacturer
Marcy Standard Weight Bench with Butterfly and Leg Developer Home Gym MD-389 
The Marcy Standard Weight Bench with Butterfly and Leg Developer MD-389 gives an intense total body workout in the comfort of your own home. The set offers a 4-position back pad that you can easily adjust to various workout out positions to perform chest and other upper body exercises such as seated presses and curls. With the inclusion of proper padding and high density upholstery, the MD-389 provides the necessary comfort to keep you training as long as you need to. The standard weight bench is designed to last longer through rigorous workouts with its powder-coated heavy duty steel frame. This equipment is a great addition to your home gym if you want to achieve the perfect muscular body. This all-in-one set is an ideal choice for any level user looking to building, toning, and maintaining muscle mass. 
Butterfly Arms 
Unlike most other benches, the Marcy Diamond Elite Standard Weight Bench MD-389 includes Butterfly Arms. Add weight plates to the post and you can do Butterfly Presses / Flys as you would at the gym. 
Preacher Curl Pad and Curl Handle 
The Marcy Diamond Elite Standard Weight Bench includes a Preacher Curl Pad and Curl Handle. To do Preacher Curls, simply add weight plates to the post below the Curl Handle and you’re set! 
Adjustable Back Pad 
Utilize the adjustable back pad to change up your workout. By inclining your back pad, you can target different parts of your muscles during Bench Presses or Flys. 
Preacher Curls 
Preacher Curls are similar to Curls. However, the Preacher Curl Pad helps you target your biceps while Curling – the Preacher Curl Pad prevents you from “cheating” during Curls.Dual-function leg developer for hamstrings, quadriceps, and glutes with four contoured foam roller pads to assist proper leg workouts. 
Leg Extensions 
The Marcy Diamond Elite Standard Weight Bench MD-389 provides a full body workout using the included leg developer. Work out your hamstrings with Leg Curls or your quadriceps with Leg Extensions. 
Butterfly Press / Flys 
Once only relegated to larger machines or club gyms, the Marcy Diamond Elite Standard Weight Bench MD-389 allows for Butterfly Presses / Flys to target your chest muscles in your home gym.

title: Home Gym Multifunctional Exercise Equipment with 143 LBS Weight Stack,Pulley System, Fly Chest, and Leg Press Gym Equipment for Home Full Body Workout Machine
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Home Gym Systems
features: My name is Jennifer, and this is my first month using my cable machine home gym. As a busy professional, I've always wanted to be able to work out my whole body at home—not just by running or doing simple yoga routines. So, I began searching for gym equipment that could meet all my full-body training needs.

After careful comparison, I finally decided on this multi-functional fitness equipment, primarily because of its wide range of workout options and customizable adjustment features. First, it’s equipped with 13 weight pieces totaling 143 pounds, with adjustable weights that suit not only me but also my husband and family, meeting various fitness levels.

With this gym equipment, I do chest flys, leg training, pull-ups, low rows, chest presses, shoulder presses, leg extensions, and more. It allows me to comprehensively train my chest, back, legs, and even smaller muscles like abs and calves. It really covers everything, helping me achieve the results I want.

My family and I particularly appreciate the flexibility of this functional trainer. For instance, the butterfly arms can be adjusted to three levels, the leg press has adjustable height and forward-backward options, and the seat cushion can be set at four levels, providing a different support experience every time and making each workout comfortable and natural.

I also found that the L-shaped steel butterfly arm structure makes the setup very stable. The seat cushion is made from soft materials, so even during long workouts, it’s still comfortable. Most notably, the leg support and curl pad are detachable, so we can store them when not in use to save space. The pulley system of lat pulldown machines is specially designed to operate smoothly and quietly, so I don’t have to worry about disturbing my family.
A few days after buying it, I received the four packages shipped separately. With the detailed installation manual and tools, my husband and I only took a few hours to set it up—easy and convenient.

Now, I work out on this all in one gym every day, and I can already feel significant changes in my body. My husband also loves it; we take turns using it daily and enjoy sharing the fun of working out and the health benefits together. I’m so glad I chose this product. It not only provides a high-quality workout experience but also brings a positive, healthy activity into our home.

Marcy SM-4008 Combo Smith Machine 
All-In-One Home Gym 
Get serious about getting in shape with the Marcy SM-4008 Combo Smith Machine. This all-in-one, home gym equipment power house, offers everything you need to tone and strengthen all major muscle groups. 
Versatile - Comprehensive Exercise Options 
A Smith-style press bar with adjustable safety stops allows you to perform a variety of powerful strength training workouts, an independent motion upper pulley system allows for cable crossover possibilities, a pull-up bar allows you to bulk up your upper body, a total leg developer allows you to strengthen lower body muscle groups and a multi-position back pad offers a safe training experience.

Top/low cable system 
Pull-up bar

Chest fly station 
Multi-position bench 
Pop-pin knob

4 storage posts

Bar Catches and Safety Catches 
The Marcy Smith Machine Home Gym includes bar catches and safety catches for free weight Olympic Bar workouts including squats and bench presses. 
Adjustable Bench

Included Accessories

Smith Machine Squats

Leg Developer Workouts – Leg Extensions

features: SMITH MACHINE: DONOW power rack is a combination of a smith machine, squat rack, chest station and lat pull down pulley system. This all-in-one gym cage features a variety of fitness exercises to tone and strengthens the core, thighs, arms, and legs.

SAFER POWER RACK: This power cage is fitted with one fixed smith bar and two solid smith bars guide-rods with safety hook, which provides you safer and more efficient workout experience in your home gym or office.

MULTIFUNCTION POWE CAGE: The high and low pulleys offer a wide range of upper and lower body exercises for a strong and confident physique. Build up your chest, shoulders, back, biceps, triceps, and abdomen using the cable pulleys to target all muscles.

HIGH QUALITY SQUAT RACK – This training machine is made with a commercial-grade solid steel frame to ensure years of use, making it a versatile machine that gives you the ability to exercise in the comfort of your home or office.

title: TRX All-in-One Suspension Training System for Weight Training, Cardio, Cross-Training & Resistance Training, Full-Body Workouts for Home, Travel, and Outdoors, Includes Indoor & Outdoor Anchor System
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Suspension Trainers
features: HOME GYM EQUIPMENT: TRX’s All-in-One Suspension Trainer System has revolutionized personal fitness. It’s designed for full-body training workouts anywhere, anytime, using only your bodyweight. The kit includes the All-in-One Suspension Trainer, Indoor/Outdoor Anchors, and a Mesh Travel Bag.

BEYOND GYM STRAPS: This TRX home workout system will allow you to achieve the results you want. You will build muscle, burn fat, strengthen your core, increase cardio endurance, and improve flexibility efficiently to transform the way you look, feel, and think.

WORKOUT ANYWHERE: TRX easily anchors to doors, rafters, or beams at home—as well as to trees, poles, or posts. Take the TRX All-in-One Suspension Training System to the beach, park, hotel, mountain, or anywhere you love to work out.

SAFETY TESTED: TRX is safety tested to support weight up to 700 lbs. TRX has been used for over 10 years by the US Military, Pro Sports teams, and world-class athletes worldwide and comes with our full TRX two-year Superior Quality Warranty.

YOUR TRIAL TO THE TRX TRAINING CLUB APP: Experience unlimited access to 500+ on-demand workouts: weight training, cardio, cross-training, sport athleticism, resistance and mobility training, and prehab and rehab. Find 100s of workouts for every goal! All workouts are guided by world-class certified TRX trainers.
NOTE: You no longer need a Key To Free Card to access our TRX Training Club App. You can download the app and access your free trial.

title: Wall Mount Cable Machine, LAT Pulldown Machines with 19 Positions Dual Pulley System, Cable Crossover Machine with Adjustable Footplate, Weight Workout Equipment Home Gym Station

breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: 【Powerful Load Capacity】This wall mount cable machine is made from high-density carbon steel, ensuring outstanding stability and strength. Equipped with aviation-grade cables, it boasts a tensile strength of up to 2200 lbs, and the dual cable system can easily support a maximum load of 400 lbs.

【Upgraded Design】This lat pulldown machines features a dual cable and pulley system with 19 adjustable height positions, perfectly meeting the demands of various fitness movements. The top and bottom mounting brackets can rotate 360 degrees, allowing installation at any angle and seamlessly integrating with the wall.

【Space-Saving】With dimensions of 27.2” (L) x 18.1” (W) x 81.9”(H), the cable machine home gym occupies just 3.42 square feet of floor space. The adjustable footplate can be lowered when not in use, ensuring it sits flush with the ground and takes up no additional space.

【Customizable】This cable workout machine comes with a weight bar compatible with both 1-inch and 2-inch weight plates for convenient weight adjustments. It includes four locking clips to secure the weight plates and prevent slipping, three adjustable hooks for length adjustments, and two single strap handles to accommodate your personalized needs.

【Multi-Functional Home Fitness】The advanced pulley design of lat pulldown machine is intended to stretch and strengthen major muscle groups, offering a variety of exercise options including tricep extensions, bicep curls, shoulder presses, squats, reverse flys, lunges, chest presses, rowing, abdominal curls, lat pulldowns, single-arm rows, and face pulls, providing you with a comprehensive and effective workout experience.
Feel free to reach out with any questions about the product, and we will respond quickly within 24 hours (on business days).

title: Body-Solid Pro ClubLine (LVBP) Adjustable Leverage Gym Bench - Converging Chest & Bench Press Machine with Sealed Bearings and Gas-Assisted Start Positions
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Benches › Adjustable Benches
description: The Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Bench Press (LVBP) is designed for serious, heavy lifting in professional gyms or at home. A converging press arm and independent, unilateral arm action deliver balanced muscle development for the upper body. Ergonomically designed multi-grips offer different positional options, with gas-assisted start positions to get your lift started right. The press arms are adjustable to fit users of all sizes. With a 2- by 3-inch 11-gauge high-tensile-strength steel mainframe and durable double-stitched upholstery, this leverage bench press machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. Sealed bearing pivot points provide smooth, friction-free movement through every intense workout. Weight plate holders are built into the machine for easy storage (plates sold separately). When assembled, the Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Bench Press measures 69 by 53 by 30 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 154 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home Warranty and Full Commercial Warranty.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

PERFECT FOR ANY SIZE USER: Enhanced with Gas-Assisted Adjustable Bench Press, Ergonomic Grip Positions, and Independent Arm Movement, this Machine Offers Tailored Chest and uper body workouts for Users of Any Size, Ensuring a Personalized and Effective Fitness Experience.

MAXIMIZE YOUR WORKOUTS: With the versatility of the Leverage Gym, you can seamlessly transition between exercises like the incline chest press, wide body bench presses, and bench press workouts. The plate-loaded design allows for precision weight adjustments, ensuring you can challenge yourself at every level of fitness. .

DURABLE AND SAFE: Experience the pinnacle of home gym equipment with the Body Solid Leverage Gym, boasting sealed bearing pivot points and weight plate holders for secure storage. The adjustable press arms, complete with durable double stitched upholstery, ensure a comfortable, safe, and stable workout tailored to your body's needs.
DIMENSIONS: Crafted with a robust 2" x 3" 11 gauge steel mainframe and coated with an electrostatically applied powder coat finish in metallic silver. Measures 69"x53"x30" and weighs 169lbs.

title: Hydrow Pro Rowing Machine with Immersive 22" HD Rotating Screen - Stows Upright | Live and On-Demand at-Home Workouts, Membership Required
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Cardio Training › Rowers
description: Working out at home is a whole lot more exciting when you’re transported to, say, a Scandinavian fjord. Hydrow’s immersive experience takes you all around the world for full-body workouts – over 5,000, to be exact – led by world-class Athletes in stunning destinations. With a proprietary computer-controlled electromagnetic drag mechanism designed to mimic the feel of rowing on water, getting onto the Hydrow Pro feels about as close as it gets to really getting out there.
features: WORK MORE MUSCLES IN LESS TIME. Build with low-impact workouts that engage more than 86% of your muscles in under 20 (yes, 20!) minutes.

GET A MEMBERSHIP, THEN GET STARTED. For just $44/month, unlock over 5,000 at-home workouts for all fitness levels. Explore a range of workout styles, including cardio, strength, recovery, and more — all led by world-class instructors in stunning locations around the world. (NOTE: Memberships are sold separately from Hydrow rowing machines.)

ESCAPE INTO IMMERSIVE WORKOUTS. Featuring a crystal-clear 22” HD rotating touchscreen display with front-facing speakers, rowing on the Hydrow Pro rower is sure to take you places. Even better – the rower itself is designed to make indoor rowing feel like on-the-water rowing, thanks to our proprietary electromagnetic drag technology. Features include padded seat, adjustable foot straps, and a low-stress grip handle.

FITS RIGHT IN AT HOME. This foldable rowing machine can be stored upright using our Upright Storage Kit (sold separately). Dimensions: 86” L x 25” W x 47” H; Weight: 145 lbs; Weight limit up to 375 pounds.
CONNECT WITH YOUR GO-TO DEVICES. The Hydrow Pro at-home rower is compatible with bluetooth-based fitness devices like Apple Watch, heart-rate monitors, and wireless headphones.

features: 【Target Your Upper Chest】Our V2 incline bench press machine is specifically designed with a 30° incline angle, widely recognized as the best angle for upper chest workouts. 【7+5 Fully Adjustable】5 Exercise Starting Position: The machine is equipped with an adjustable seat(5 positions), which allows you to easily adapt the device to the height of the exerciser. Thanks to the adjustable backrest angle, the machine offers 7 exercise starting positions. Such variety allows you to increase the effectiveness of each workout and build chest sculpture faster.

【Special Gas-Spring Design】Are you still struggling with adjusting the height of the work arms? Our machine will solve your problem perfectly with a unique gas-spring design. Simply A PRESS (press on the arms) and A PULL (pull out the pin), and the work arms will automatically rise. Release the pin when arms reach the desired position. No longer face the inconvenience of manually adjusting the height with your two hands. Note: Avoid putting too much weight on it; the best use is with an empty arm.

【Independent Converging Work Arms】The biggest surprise is that the arms are independent and cylinder design on each arm for easy adjustment. Can provide unilateral training to ensure muscle symmetry. Fit for beginners and regular gym-goers alike!

Why do we say that our machine is also suitable for beginners? 
V2 incline press machine can be suitable for beginners as it provides a guided movement and allows for easy adjustments to the weight and angle. 
Can the incline chest press machine help strengthen other muscles besides the chest? 
Certainly, the incline press machine primarily works the chest muscles (pectoralis major and minor), as well as the triceps and shoulders. It can also engage the core muscles as you stabilize your body during the exercise. 
Why should I consider using this incline bench press machine? 
Specifically designed with a 30° incline angle, widely recognized as the best angle for upper chest workouts, and with other 6 backrest positions to choose, our machine helps to build your chest sculpture faster. 
Why choose this machine with vertical grip options? 
Verticval grips can offer better ergonomic support, reducing strain on wrist, elbow and shoulder. With vertical grips, you can also allow for targeting upper chest more precisely, enhancing the overall effectiveness of your fitness routine.

Transform Your Home Gym, Transform Your Body 
The Smith machine is a piece of equipment commonly used in home gyms for a full body workout. It can be especially helpful for women or beginners who are new to the gym. The equipment has a barbell supported on each side and a pulley system that moves the weights. The bar moves up and down on a track, and safety bars restrict the bar from moving further than desired. The springs in the smith machine also absorb some impact, preventing injuries. 
There are several reasons why one might use a Smith machine, including: 
To become familiar with a specific exercise and its proper form before attempting it with free weights.
To isolate a particular group of muscles for strength training or to address muscle imbalances.
To prepare for an exercise that you are not yet able to do with free weights.
To alleviate nervousness about trying free weight movements, such as squats, deadlifts, or hip thrusts, for the first time.
To practice the movement pattern and foot placement and get comfortable with the bar without having to manage a standard 45-pound barbell on your shoulders or in your hands.
The Smith machine can be used in conjunction with other fitness equipment and accessories, such as a workout bench, squat rack, cable attachments, and a pull-up bar, to provide more exercise options. One can use a functional trainer with the Smith machine to do basic exercises such as cable fly, lat pulldown, horizontal bar and parallel bars, low bar pull-up, barbell deadlift, barbell squat, push-up, and pull-up. The workout bench provides more workout options, including seated leg extension, lying leg extension, upper body stretches, and incline, decline, and flat barbell chest press. The Smith machine can also be used as part of an all-in-one cage or Altas Strength home gym equipment, which includes a leg press, arm curl, and other attachments. 
Overall, the Smith machine is an excellent choice for those looking to exercise at home, as it provides a safe and effective way to target various muscle groups while minimizing the risk of injury.

One can use a functional trainer with the Smith machine to do basic exercises such as cable fly, lat pulldown, horizontal bar and parallel bars, low bar pull-up, barbell deadlift, barbell squat, push-up, and pull-up. The workout bench provides more workout options, including seated leg extension, lying leg extension, upper body stretches, and incline, decline, and flat barbell chest press. The Smith machine can also be used as part of an all-in-one cage or Altas Strength home gym equipment, which includes a leg press, arm curl, and other attachments. 
Overall, the Smith machine is an excellent choice for those looking to exercise at home, as it provides a safe and effective way to target various muscle groups while minimizing the risk of injury. 
Discover the versatility of the Smith machine with exercises like squats, hip thrusts, deadlifts, shoulder press, and more. Learn proper form, bar weight details, comparisons with free weights, and considerations for effective workouts. Whether at a gym or home gym, find insights on the Smith machine's benefits, setup, and best practices for a well-rounded strength training routine.

modules.title: Unleash your potential with Altas Strength Smith Machine 3059. Build strength, sculpt muscles, and achieve your fitness goals. Gym essential!  Why You Should Give The Smith Machine A Try? It can help all Home Gym levels, from beginners to advanced athletes wanting to perform better.
modules.text:
A Smith Machine is good for prepping your body for heavy weight training or giving extra assistance when you have a weaker side or muscle. You can implement it into squats, deadlifts, hip thrusts, bench presses, and bicep curls. 
Smith machines make Home Gym easier, especially if you are a woman or new to the gym. 
The smith machine with a barbell supported on each side and a pulley system moving the weights. Because the bar is moving on a track, it can only move up and down. Safety bars restrict the bar from moving further than you would like, and springs absorb some impacts when dropped, keeping you from getting injured. 
You can use a smith machine for the following reasons: 
To get familiar with a specific exercise and its form thereof before trying it with free weights
To isolate a particular group of muscles for strength purposes or because of muscle imbalances
To prepare you for an exercise that you are unable to do
Familiarize Yourself With An Exercise On The Smith Machine 
To get rid of the jitters you might have about trying a free weight movement. Squat, deadlifts, or hip thrusts can be very intimidating, especially if you have never done it before.
To identify the movement pattern and the placement of your feet and get the feel of the bar without having to manage a standard barbell of 45 pounds on your shoulders or in your hands.

features: [Versatile Upper Body Training Machine]- The seated triceps dip machine allows for focused and isolated workouts. Its convergent motion ensures that the triceps muscles are activated for maximum exercise effectiveness. In addition, the triceps press machine comes with a cable bar for doing biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls. It's a versatile machine that engages the muscles of the arms, shoulder and chest to take your upper body strength training to the next level!

[Improved Arms and Machine Design]- The seated dip machine is a safer and more effective alternative to traditional tricep dips, which can cause strain on the wrists and shoulders. With stable and controllable movements, this seated dip station minimizes the risk of injuries. Additionally, the tricep pushdown machine features a rotating handle that can be adjusted to fit varying shoulder widths, providing multiple grip options to target different areas of the triceps muscles.

[Personalized Adjustments]- It offers easy-to-use personalization adjustments, allowing you to customize your workout to suit your varying fitness levels and training goals with simple weight plate adjustments. Even beginners can experience challenging workouts without requiring extensive technical skills or coordination. The seat height and cable bar length can be adjusted to accommodate different body types, ensuring maximum comfort and efficiency during your exercise routine.

[High Quality Material]- The plate loaded tricep machine is composed of heavy-duty steel and premium coatings, making it durable and stable. The comfortable, sweat-resistant seat and backrest provide ample support for intense workouts and long-term use. Measuring only 42.7"x26.2"x51.2", it's the ideal size for any space in your home gym. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 LBS and compatibility with 1" and 2" weight plates, it can meet your most daily training needs. (Plates are not included)

[Easy to Use Step]- The tricep press machine is also featured by simplicity in use. To give your triceps a serious workout, all you need to do is choose the right weights, adjust the seat height, and grab onto the narrow handles. If you want to give your lower chest muscles some extra attention, just lean forward ever so slightly and switch to the wide handle. To perform a bicep curl, rise to your feet and plant them firmly on a rugged steel plate, then you can exercise freely with cable handle.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Check it out! The Panther is the ultimate destination for your home gym journey 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Does this machine come with all the bells and whistles, or do I have to buy extra stuff? 
Oh, it’s got all the bells and whistles, my friend. No need to go hunting for extra gear. You’ve got your Smith machine, pec deck, cable pulley system, pull-up bars... it’s a one-stop shop for your entire workout. Just bring your muscles. 
What’s with the 7-degree angled Smith machine? Does that actually make a difference? 
Oh yeah, big time! That 7-degree angle isn’t just for looks—it’s all about smoother, more natural movement. No more “joint grinds” that feel like you’re wrestling with the machine. You’ll feel like you're lifting with the pros. 
Can I actually fit this beast in my garage, or is it gonna need its own room? 
It’s a powerhouse, but we designed it to save space. Think of it like a Transformer—big performance, compact design. It'll fit in your garage or home gym without turning it into a circus tent. 
What’s the deal with the cable ratios? 
No calculators needed! Here's the breakdown: 
4:1 on the pulley system 
2:1 on the pec deck 
1:1 on the low row 
Mix these ratios, and you’ve got versatile training for every muscle, every angle. It’s like having a whole gym in one machine! 
Is the pec deck on this machine really as good as it sounds, or is it just a gimmick? 
Nope, no gimmicks here! The built-in pec deck is smooth, comfy, and hits your chest just right. Adjustable settings let you customize for the perfect stretch and contraction. It's like having a trainer, minus the sweat!

Can the ShredForce be used for leg workouts too? 
No - the ShredForce is specifically made to help you train your upper body, so it won't be safe to use as a leg trainer. 
When storing my ShredForce, should it be open or closed? 
The best way to store it is to lower the resistance level and close the arm exerciser. This way your hydraulics will stay in outstanding condition for much longer. 
Do the hydraulics on the exerciser leak oil during training? 
Absolutely not. The premium hydraulics built into the ShredForce are durable and made to feel absolutely outstanding during workouts - no leaks, no other issues. 
Who can benefit from the ShredForce? 
The compact form combined with a wide resistance range makes the ShredForce a great option for traveling athletes, people just getting back into training, folks who live in smaller spaces, and anyone who needs an extra boost of upper body strength. 
Will the ShredForce replace my dumbbells? 
While most people will be perfectly satisfied with the upper body workouts they can perform with the Shredforce, it isn't made to be a direct replacement for dumbbells, but rather a complement that covers the needs your dumbbells don't.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Chest Press Machine with Independent Converging Arms for a Unique Workout 
Adjustable Flat or Incline Chest Bench Press with Ab Crunch Feature 
The extra long seat pad allows the user to adjust their position for a different range of motion or to target the muscles from a different angle. The high-density, dual-layered pad folds down for the incline bench feature and acts as an ab crunch board. The foam ankle pads secure the user and support ankles and knees when performing ab crunches. The safety catches allow each arm to be rested when not in use and protect the user in the event the lift cannot be completed. Each safety catch, featuring a protective rubber strip, has 9 different adjustment positions using a locking pin, allowing an 8” range. A plate storage peg is featured on both sides of the unit to allow a clean and organized home gym. 
Each weight & storage peg measures 8” long and 1” in diameter. To convert plate storage pegs to 2" for Olympic style plates, the EX-10 adaptor is sold separately. 
This weight bench station has a Maximum Weight load of 125 lbs per arm, allowing users to train with up to 250 lbs. total. 
Maximize Your Home Gym Workout - Upper Body & Core Routines 
Flat Bench- Chest Press 
Flat bench presses are best for overall development of the pectoralis, commonly known as the pecs or your chest muscles. With this natural and fluid movement, it is likely to assist you in daily life activities as well as other exercises! 
Incline Bench - Chest Press 
With a similar movement to the flat bench, performing incline bench presses will activate your shoulders as well as the upper part of the pecs. The incline press puts less strain on your rotator cuff while activating the deltoids. 
Ab Crunch Feature 
Using the high density pad supports by the head of the bench, you can secure yourself by placing your feet behind them and perform ab crunches while the bench is in the incline position, allowing you to add more variation to your workout!

Its increased stability provides more focus and juice to the targeted muscles because stabilizing muscles are not used. Due to your path of motion is fixed. Essentially, you can hone in on the muscle for added volume and activation. 
How this Machine Helps You to Build a Nice-Shaping Rear Delts? 
It isolates the rear delts and muscles of the upper back without using stabilizing muscles of the lower body. You also use the pad to rest your chest against for leverage, which allows you to reverse fly with a greater load. 
Pec and Rear Delt machine vs Function trainer! Why do you shoulder-pick this for a Chest or Rear Delt Workout?
